## üìö ‡∏Ñ‡∏≥‡∏™‡∏±‡πà‡∏á‡∏ó‡∏±‡πâ‡∏á‡∏´‡∏°‡∏î

### Package Management

```bash
mrg install <package>       # ‡∏ï‡∏¥‡∏î‡∏ï‡∏±‡πâ‡∏á package
mrg i <package>             # ‡∏ï‡∏¥‡∏î‡∏ï‡∏±‡πâ‡∏á (‡πÅ‡∏ö‡∏ö‡∏™‡∏±‡πâ‡∏ô)
mrg i pkg1 pkg2 pkg3        # ‡∏ï‡∏¥‡∏î‡∏ï‡∏±‡πâ‡∏á‡∏´‡∏•‡∏≤‡∏¢ packages ‡∏û‡∏£‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏°‡∏Å‡∏±‡∏ô
mrg uninstall <package>     # ‡∏ñ‡∏≠‡∏ô‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏ï‡∏¥‡∏î‡∏ï‡∏±‡πâ‡∏á
mrg list                    # ‡πÅ‡∏™‡∏î‡∏á packages ‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡∏ï‡∏¥‡∏î‡∏ï‡∏±‡πâ‡∏á
mrg search <keyword>        # ‡∏Ñ‡πâ‡∏ô‡∏´‡∏≤ packages
mrg info <package>          # ‡∏î‡∏π‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏°‡∏π‡∏• package
mrg update                  # ‡∏≠‡∏±‡∏û‡πÄ‡∏î‡∏ó package registry
```

### Running

```bash
mrg run <file.mrg>          # ‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ô‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå .mrg
```

### Information

```bash
mrg version                 # ‡πÄ‡∏ä‡πá‡∏Ñ‡πÄ‡∏ß‡∏≠‡∏£‡πå‡∏ä‡∏±‡∏ô
mrg help                    # ‡∏î‡∏π‡∏Ñ‡∏≥‡∏™‡∏±‡πà‡∏á‡∏ó‡∏±‡πâ‡∏á‡∏´‡∏°‡∏î
```

## üì¶ Packages ‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡∏°‡∏µ

- **discord.mrg** - Discord Bot Module
- **http.mrg** - HTTP Client
- **file.mrg** - File System Operations
- **json.mrg** - JSON Parser
- **database.mrg** - SQLite Database
- **math.mrg** - Math Functions
- **crypto.mrg** - Cryptography
- **image.mrg** - Image Processing

## üìñ ‡∏ï‡∏±‡∏ß‡∏≠‡∏¢‡πà‡∏≤‡∏á‡πÄ‡∏û‡∏¥‡πà‡∏°‡πÄ‡∏ï‡∏¥‡∏°

### HTTP Request

```mrg
import http.mrg

command ‡∏£‡∏≤‡∏Ñ‡∏≤‡∏ö‡∏¥‡∏ó‡∏Ñ‡∏≠‡∏¢‡∏ô‡πå
    response = http get https://api.coindesk.com/v1/bpi/currentprice.json
    reply ‡∏£‡∏≤‡∏Ñ‡∏≤‡∏ö‡∏¥‡∏ó‡∏Ñ‡∏≠‡∏¢‡∏ô‡πå: {response.bpi.USD.rate} USD
```

### File Operations

```mrg
import file.mrg

