    file write data.txt ‡∏™‡∏ß‡∏±‡∏™‡∏î‡∏µ‡∏à‡∏≤‡∏Å MRG
    reply ‡∏ö‡∏±‡∏ô‡∏ó‡∏∂‡∏Å‡∏™‡∏≥‡πÄ‡∏£‡πá‡∏à!
```

### Database

```mrg
